document_data.name: House of the Master's Shadow
document_data.mainbody: The '''House of the Master's Shadow''' was a temple of [[Mask]] in [[Uthmere]]. The House was hidden in the worst part of town, led by the [[Shadowmasters of Telflamm]].<ref name=UE-p127>
